botocore (1.40.61-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of botocore 1.40.61 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of aiobotocore (Avalan's `vendors`
    extra, reached via aioboto3). Noble ships 1.34.46+repack and
    the Debian snapshot pool has no version in aiobotocore's
    `>=1.40.46,<1.40.62` window; pinned from the upstream PyPI
    sdist at 1.40.61, the top of the window.
  * No source patches required: upstream's setup.py is the sole
    build entry point and Noble's setuptools 68 accepts it as-is.

